.el .ds Aq '
.TH aisw 1  "aisw 0.1.0" 
.SH NAME
aisw \- Manage multiple accounts for Claude Code, Codex CLI, and Gemini CLI
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBaisw\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage multiple accounts for Claude Code, Codex CLI, and Gemini CLI
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
aisw\-add(1)
Add a new account profile for a tool
.TP
aisw\-use(1)
Switch the active account for a tool
.TP
aisw\-list(1)
Show all profiles, optionally filtered by tool
.TP
aisw\-remove(1)
Remove a stored profile
.TP
aisw\-rename(1)
Rename a stored profile
.TP
aisw\-status(1)
Show current active profiles and credential status
.TP
aisw\-init(1)
First\-run setup: shell integration and credential import
.TP
aisw\-shell\-hook(1)
Print the shell integration hook for the given shell
.TP
aisw\-backup(1)
Manage credential backups
.TP
aisw\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH VERSION
v0.1.0
